@startuml
title State Diagram: Scene Integration Lifecycle

top to bottom direction

[*] --> Uninitialized : Start App

Uninitialized --> ScenePathSet : loadScene(path)
ScenePathSet --> DataParsed : parseSceneData()
DataParsed --> SceneInitialized : initializeScene()

SceneInitialized --> ModelsLoaded : ModelImporter.loadModels()
ModelsLoaded --> MaterialsApplied : MaterialHandler.applyMaterials()

MaterialsApplied --> LightingSet : LightingManager.setupDefaultLighting()
LightingSet --> EnvironmentApplied : EnvironmentHandler.applyHDRI(path)

EnvironmentApplied --> ControlsInitialized : OrbitControlsHandler.initialize()
ControlsInitialized --> ReadyToRender : System is ready

ReadyToRender --> Rendering : Renderer.render()
Rendering --> FrameRendered : onFrameComplete()
FrameRendered --> ReadyToRender : loop

@enduml
